# GetName

**Instance Method**

Gets the name of the object.

## Declaration

```swift
OSSharedPtr<OSString> GetName();
```

## Return Value

A `OSSharedPtr` to an [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/DriverKit/OSString] containing the object name.

## Discussion

Getting the name synchronizes by using the work queue created by the object.

## Working with Object Names

- **SetName**: Sets the name of the object.
